{"tid":1927942,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼幫推] 警告！！連登進入緊急狀態！！","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T06:40:02.000Z","uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8d183d17244e1e0dc0fe4168ee818f16e91c6a","tid":1927942,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"選戰臨近，公關公司空群而出<br />\n<br />\n熱門不斷被無聊 post 長期佔據<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特此宣佈連登進入緊急狀態，直至選舉完結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所有手足，包括黃絲連登 admin 必須立即採取以下措施，防止連登淪陷<br />\n<br />\n1、凡見熱門有膠 post 淫 post 等與抗爭無關者，一律舉報<br />\n<br />\n2、若有黃絲 admin 發現有會員經常開無聊 post 而上熱門者，請調查其真實身份是否涉及紅色資本所聘請之公關公司，掌握證據後請立即封鎖其帳戶<br />\n<br />\n3、所有手足只推行動及文宣 post , 其他一律推文<br />\n<br />\n4、所有會員自律，唔好開同推無聊 post<br />\n<br />\n事關重大，香港前途就係大家手上<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民參政 光復議會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1927507/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1927507/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇得出今次真係好大件事 大家打醒十二分精神"},{"pid":"fddefbfeeee04df13a43969c77d8e777145d0ed2","tid":1927942,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"29ed7d13ad5988a617fb262a7949afcae5984bc8","tid":1927942,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"有用post要推!!"},{"pid":"450cd0caf69b40e16f53adca3441f73a18acc796","tid":1927942,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"看完你會感激我，一鍵按走膠po廢文的連登隱藏設定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1927900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1927900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"876abd0f5944666857f57195e9e4ffaea9d3e0d7","tid":1927942,"uid":48317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"唔啦 J下囡囡好過"},{"pid":"41527db172fdd003e1fbab